OL,3,CIncoming recycling rules 'unworkable'
OL,4,Csay business owners
OL,6,FBusinesses across Wales will be
OL,7,Fexpected to follow new recycling rules
OL,8,Ffrom April 6.
OL,10,FThe aim is to boost national rates,
OL,11,Fbut many business owners say the new
OL,12,Flaws are unworkable and an added
OL,13,Ffinancial strain.
OL,15,FAll businesses, charities and public
OL,16,Fsector organisations will be required
OL,17,Fby law to sort their waste for
OL,18,Frecycling.
