OL,6,FJulie Bell from the Brecon Beacons
OL,7,FTourism Association said members do
OL,8,Fwant to recycle more, however, she
OL,9,Fbelieves these new regulations need
OL,10,Fmore thought.
OL,12,F"Self-catering providers are coming to
OL,13,Fus and saying they'll have to go
OL,14,Fthrough the recycling as they would
OL,15,Ftheir own, which isn't really what you
OL,16,Fwant to be doing as you don't know
OL,17,Fwhat's going to be in some of these
OL,18,Fbins", she said.
