OL,6,F"So the whole infrastructure, it just
OL,7,Fdoesn't work at the moment. We need to
OL,8,Ffind a way to make it work."
OL,10,FWaste recycling companies have also
OL,11,Fvoiced concern as they say they don't
OL,12,Fknow how they'll increase the number
OL,13,Fof recycling lorries needed to do
OL,14,Fextra trips.
OL,16,FAware the new law will cause some
OL,17,Finitial confusion, Marten Lewis,
OL,18,FDirector of Sustainability at
OL,19,FBluestone said they have already began
OL,20,Fimplementing a segregated recycling
OL,21,Fmodel at their site.
