OL,3,CIncoming recycling rules 'unworkable'
OL,4,Csay business owners
OL,6,F"Since installing new bins across our
OL,7,Fsite for the separation of our
OL,8,Frecyclable waste, we have noticed that
OL,9,Fthere is a lot less cross
OL,10,Fcontamination. The right items are
OL,11,Fending up in the right bins, meaning
OL,12,Fthat the quality of the waste we are
OL,13,Fsending for recycling has improved by
OL,14,Fmore than half."
OL,16,FHe added: "Complying with the new law
OL,17,Fhas been simple. It has involved
OL,18,Finstalling additional bins in all our
OL,19,Flodges, as well as public areas and
OL,20,Frestaurants.
